packageJSON.name: Timesheets
packageJSON.description: A timesheet keeping app based on electron

scripts.build-main: cross-env NODE_ENV=production node -r babel-register ./node_modules/webpack/bin/webpack --config webpack.config.electron.js --progress --profile --colors && cp app/package.json dist/
scripts.build-renderer: cross-env NODE_ENV=production node -r babel-register ./node_modules/webpack/bin/webpack --config webpack.config.production.js --progress --profile --colors && cp -R app/renderer/assets dist/renderer
scripts.build: npm run build-main && npm run build-renderer
scripts.start-hot: cross-env HOT=1 NODE_ENV=development electron -r babel-register -r babel-polyfill ./app/main/index
